{"type": "article", "id": 13048, "title": "阿迪达斯的这波广告，真是充满“魔性”", "description": "画风稳定至极。", "date": "2015-08-05T09:05:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2126, "name": "曼联"}, {"id": 13996, "name": "多特蒙德"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604230701xNmGW4gUDf0YMI2a.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t阿迪达斯日前发布曼联新赛季球衣，并推出了一支主题为 <span>#BreakExpectation </span>的宣传广告，然而片中球员化身地狱红魔，手拿三叉戟<span></span>击碎屏幕的设定也引发了网友吐槽：还真是 <span>break</span>，因为你就不该有 <span>expectation</span>。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<iframe src=\"http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/html5embed.action?type=0&amp;code=Cs8_zFB209E&amp;lcode=&amp;resourceId=0_06_05_99\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t在曼联结束了和耐克 <span>13 </span>年的球衣合作之后，阿迪达斯用一个“击碎一切”的大片宣布接管红魔的球衣统治。听起来有点熟悉？<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/11614.html\" target=\"_blank\">和之前尤文图斯球衣的“烧光一切”是同一个系列。</a><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230659EurY6mvn7D0a5VCo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>曼联新版女款球衣因为领口过低引发争议</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t无论是“被嫉妒你够资格吗”，还是<span><a href=\"http://huati.weibo.com/k/%E5%BC%82%E7%B1%BB%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7?from=526\">“</a></span>异类崛起”，阿迪达斯贯彻争议话题的决心非常坚定，魔性的广告风格也一如既往的稳定（不知道为什么视频通过不了审核，只能截动图给大家看了）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140648JZ8AumeKS1lfxFUY.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"text-align:left;\" data-ratio=\"0.54173228\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261406522lEy4qbjfKtW3VNX.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54173228\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140653JQmknzOAj4SYF1fH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54173228\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230700QWRGOBhgCiwtszTS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54833597\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042307004IsDeqB5X1PM9Sn7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54833597\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140655OKkHtGoT2uZQ8MwR.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"text-align:left;\" data-ratio=\"0.54833597\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t以上画面来自 <span>#Be The Difference (</span>异类崛起<span>)</span>系列最新广告，踩扁地球、操控玩偶、以独裁者形象出现的多特蒙德队长胡梅尔斯显得控制力十足，而他在片中所穿的战靴 <span>ACE 15 </span>采用了 <span>3D </span>凸点技术，正是以良好的控球能力著称。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>另一位出镜的球员拉维奇代表的则是超轻设计 </span><span>X 15</span><span>，这位阿根廷国脚拥有出色的突破能力，阿迪达斯希望 </span><span>X 15 </span><span>能够成为那些危险球员的首选。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140659C54SJVMl7xIrjO6b.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54173228\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}